# Cookie Policy for TasksMate

Last updated: April 11, 2025

At TasksMate, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Cookie Policy explains how we use cookies and similar technologies when you use our website and services.

## What Are Cookies?

Cookies are small data files stored on your device that help websites and apps remember your preferences, login sessions, and activity.

## How We Use Cookies

TasksMate uses cookies for the following purposes:

- **Essential Cookies**: These are necessary for the website to function (e.g., login, authentication, security).
- **Performance Cookies**: These help us analyze how users interact with our platform so we can improve functionality and UX.
- **Preference Cookies**: These remember your settings and choices to personalize your experience.
- **Analytics Cookies**: We use tools like Google Analytics to collect anonymous data about traffic and usage.

## Your Choices

You can manage or disable cookies anytime via your browser settings. Please note that disabling essential cookies may affect how the platform functions.

## Third-Party Cookies

Some cookies may be set by third-party tools (like payment gateways, analytics providers, or embedded services). We do not control these cookies directly, but we only use trusted partners.

## Updates

We may update this policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page.

## Contact Us

If you have any questions about our cookie usage, contact us at [privacy@tasksmate.com](mailto:privacy@tasksmate.com).
